{"tid":2412530,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"當連登仔仲笑緊intel 14nm製程俾台積電屈機時，Apple已經瞄準Nvidia & Amd","createTime":"2021-02-18T05:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T06:58:58.000Z","uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6bbd75f33095ea45372a6754bba16a424fae425b","tid":2412530,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:41:24.000Z","msg":"2月17日，在基準測試網站CPU Monkey中發現了蘋果M1X soc的規格參數資訊。根據該網站的資料，M1X在CPU和GPU等各方面相比M1晶片都有巨大的提升。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9akVXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9akVXD.jpg&h=d4d5d52d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMonkey表示，M1X晶片大概率會於2021年第二季度發佈，2021款的MacBook Pro、MacBook Pro 16以及iMac 27都將會使用該晶片。<br />\n<br />\n從上圖可以看到，相較於M1來說，M1X晶片由8核心CPU升級為12核心CPU，使用的是8個高效能核心+4個低功耗核心的組合。<br />\n<br />\nGPU方面，M1X的GPU為16核設計，256個執行單元，提升了整整一倍。參考M1晶片2.6TFLOPS的浮點運算效能，M1X有雙倍核心就能翻倍到5.2TFLOPS，已經可以<strong><span class=\"red\">媲美GTX 1070了（6.5TFLOPS）。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至於製程工藝，M1X同樣也是5nm工藝，CPU時脈維持3.2GHz不變。<br />\n<br />\n其它方面，蘋果M1X配備了最大16GB的記憶體，還支援三個螢幕同時連接。"},{"pid":"1bb7b51909aa72bf42c55b68a33e78cac1e8b6eb","tid":2412530,"uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"Windows拿拿聲補救返arm Win10<br />\nNV想收購ARM<br />\nAMD痴埋去Samsung度搞arm soc<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff9579c6d4711bf366c5b9ac59523c53fb4491b","tid":2412530,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1bb7b51909aa72bf42c55b68a33e78cac1e8b6eb","tid":2412530,"uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"Windows拿拿聲補救返arm Win10<br />\nNV想收購ARM<br />\nAMD痴埋去Samsung度搞arm soc<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nArm <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47703ed205762a03bea9d34621546e1ebbc2e44d","tid":2412530,"uid":51747,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"圖寫最大32<br />\n字就寫16⋯"},{"pid":"ab3313236305fcd8ce22e0ad9fdee5bef4bc9470","tid":2412530,"uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":22,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:08:36.000Z","msg":"硬件台笑話分享<br />\n原來「效能消耗」同「畫質提升」不成直線正比係因為arm廢過x86<br />\n<br />\n佢知唔知PS3用PowerPC係RISC嚟？Console黑科技又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nApple M1X soc：GPU核心數量double、效能能媲美GTX 1070<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/stmjyrX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/stmjyrX</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FTsYinNC4uI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFTsYinNC4uI&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=05643ca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FTsYinNC4uI</a><br />\n<br />\nPS4 得1.84 teraflops<br />\n<br />\nPS5多過PS4 5.58倍 唔通畫面真係可以靚過佢5.58倍？？<br />\n<br />\n結論：PS5垃圾？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de46e80711c5bdd0dc9553d54bb27a80a2adcf85","tid":2412530,"uid":80650,"like":41,"dislike":12,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"冇左台積電幫手<br />\nApple咪又淨係識畫設計圖<br />\n煙條成日比人恥笑14+++++<br />\n但至少係屬於自己嘅晶圓廠，自己嘅產能<br />\n我睇好煙條幾年後會浴火重生"},{"pid":"968047a71c4721a6e9b3e6bc104f2c3584f206a9","tid":2412530,"uid":51183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"有無人用M1 挖礦先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b65ffefe713a1d331f93ed9a1e23a49a5ecaa6","tid