e feedback that customers would like to see those x64 apps running on ARM64. That&rsquo;s why we are working on expanding the capability of our emulation to include x64 applications and sharing this first preview to gather feedback."},{"pid":"560a770a9c6abd4351c1a70b3f952cef069a7378","tid":2412530,"uid":385412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cced8dc24fbf91a31e520a432c29132cb23aeae","tid":2412530,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e2d54c08717e8bb90111c6ddd4074c8d1945927","tid":2412530,"uid":385412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef14c676aa0c48495e7527586f756bbe8c01467f","tid":2412530,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"14000砌rtx 3080 其他野究竟要幾慳皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"你原價買到3080咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"原價買都唔撚得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"好多non-OC aib 都係8k有找姐（原價）其他位唔使Cheap out 好多嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cf0b1bb50aff7a517371b45e0a28ca42a60edf","tid":2412530,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deb02549423c6e929d7632675e78f31499bbe159","tid":2412530,"uid":124690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:17:39.000Z","msg":"其實一路都有啲傻鳩話arm 邊有本事做到高性能<br />\n<br />\n我想講如果基於x86開發，再用arm行佢咪有折損囉<br />\n<br />\n如果成個software 由頭到尾都係arm 開發，問題何在"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-